description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 21, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 63, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 2 for East, Stringalong for South, and Nine Lives for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40213-82792-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [63 Votes, Common]
